WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'Ballounes' is a Workbench game in which you have to burst
balloons, balls, bubbles or whatever the term you use (here in
the Quebec province, we use the French term 'Balloune' and it
is pronounced about this way: "Bah-loon"), these are the round
coloured objects that appear on the game board.

  You get points if there are balloons of the same colour next to
the balloon that burst; those balloons will also burst and so on,
creating a chain reaction. If no balloons of the same colour are
next to the burst balloon, two (2) new balloons will appear on the
game board.

  As the game progress, special tiles (blocks, tiles that generate
lightning bolts, exploding tiles, etc.) will appear from time to
time on the game board...

  Do not let the board fill up completely because if it happens,
the game will be over.

  Have fun!

